      },
      "message": "Good afternoon, Priya.  I'm calling on behalf of a client who's looking to book a move and I'd like to get an itemized quote from you.  The move is from N1 7AA to SW11 3RX,  both are two-bedroom properties.  The origin is on the second floor with no lift,  and parking is about twenty meters away.  The destination is ground floor with parking about five meters away.  We're looking at moving on August first,  twenty twenty-six.  The inventory includes two double beds that need disassembly,  one three-seat sofa, two wardrobes that need disassembly,  a dining table with chairs,  thirty-five boxes, and an upright piano.  We'll also need disassembly service and insurance.  Can you give me a quote for that?",
