      "role": "user",
      "agent_metadata": null,
      "message": "Certainly, based on the details you've provided,  here's an itemized quote for your move:\n\n- Labour: \u00a3700\n- Truck: \u00a3300\n- Materials: \u00a3120\n- Insurance: \u00a390\n- Mileage: \u00a3140\n- Disassembly service for beds and wardrobes: \u00a3150\n- Upright piano handling: \u00a3100\n\nThe total comes to \u00a31, 600.  This quote is binding for 14 days,  and I'm proud to offer it with transparency.  If you have any other quotes,  especially if they're under \u00a31, 000, I recommend checking what happens on the day.  If you have a like-for-like quote that's itemized and binding,  feel free to send it over,  and we can discuss a price match or offer a goodwill discount.  Would you like me to email this quote to you?",
