      "message": "Thank you for the breakdown,  Priya \u2014 I appreciate the transparency.   Just to clarify,  is there anything that could cause the final bill to be higher than this sixteen hundred pounds on the day of the move?   And you mentioned my client has some flexibility on the move date \u2014 if we could shift to a weekday or off-peak time,   would that change the price at all?",
