    {
      "role": "user",
      "agent_metadata": null,
      "message": "That's a very good question. The quote I've provided is binding for 14 days, meaning as long as the details of the move remain exactly as you've described, the final bill will be \u00a31,600.  We pride ourselves on transparency, so there won't be any hidden charges on the day, provided there are no changes to the inventory or access conditions.\n\nRegarding your second question about shifting the move date to a weekday or off-peak time, our pricing is already set to be fair and competitive.  While some companies might offer different rates for off-peak times, our structure is designed to provide consistent value.  Therefore, moving to a weekday or off-peak time wouldn't significantly alter this particular quote.",
